Item.name: Ukushayela okwamanje. Indlela eya ebhodini lokunamathisela
Faka ikhodi ku-UCS-2 BE BE BOM
Nika amandla isitayela sefonti ye-italiki jikelele
Vumela umhlaba wonke ugcizelele isitayela sefonti
Fihla ibha yemenyu (sebenzisa ukhiye we-Alt noma u-F10 ukuze uguqule)
Khubaza isici sokuphenya esiphezulu (uma unenkinga ye-touchpad)
Nika amandla ukupheqa ngaphesheya komugqa wokugcina
Vula wonke amafolda wefolda esikhundleni sokuqala ifolda njengendawo yokusebenzela kwifolda yehla
Phatha ukubuyela emuva njengendlela yokuphunyuka kwe-SQL
Nika amandla isifinyezo seseshini nokusekela ngezikhathi ezithile
Nika amandla ukuqedela ngokuzenzakalela kokufakwayo ngalunye
* Ukuguqulwa kwalesi silungiselelo kudinga ukuqala kabusha i-Notepad ++
Izilungiselelo zokukhethwa kwe-Delimiter (Ctrl + Mouse chofoza kabili)
Sebenzisa uhla lwezinhlamvu zamagama ezizenzakalelayo njengoba kunjalo
Engeza uhlamvu lwakho njengengxenye yegama (ungakhethi ngaphandle kokuthi wazi ukuthi wenzani)
SSetha indlela yakho yendawo yamafu lapha:
Bonisa kuphela igama lomsebenzisi ku-bar yesihloko

ContextMenuXmlEditWarning.title: Isimo sokuhlelaUmsebenzisi
ContextMenuXmlEditWarning.message: Isimo sokuhlelaMenu.xml ikuvumela ukuba ushintshe imenyu yakho yokuqukethwe yesikhombisi se-Notepad ++. Kufanele uqale kabusha i-Notepad ++ yakho ukuze isebenze ngemva kokuguqula umongoMenu.xml.
